import React, { useState } from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

function Navbar() {
    return ( <
        >
        <
        nav className = "navbar" >
        <
        div className = "navbar-container" >
        <
        Link to = "/"
        className = "navbar-logo" >
        TRVL < i className = "fab fa-typo3" / >
        <
        /Link> <
        /div> <
        /nav> <
        />
    )
}

export default Navbar
